            <br />
            <div class="newsticker">
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        <div class="info">
                            03/11/2012: SundBoell made changes to the service
                        </div>
                        <div class="clear">
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <div class="info">
                            03/11/2012: CMA CGM announces changes to the FAL8 service, including new ports.
